parameters.name: DiskId
parameters.description: The ID of the disk. Format: d-\*\*\*\*\*\*\*\*\*\*\*.

parameters.name: EndTime
parameters.description: The beginning of the time range to query. Specify the time in the format of yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss. The time range specified by the StartTime and EndTime parameters cannot exceed one day for a query.

parameters.name: StartTime
parameters.description: The beginning of the time range to query. Specify the time in the format of yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.
